snippet.textDisplay:
Beautiful composition..But too much additional programming done with Maithili's voice. She doesn't even complete her line and she starts with another line..kyu itna editing bhai..Vo live vaali feeling nikal gayi hai coke studio me ab bas accha kapda pehen ke muh hila rahe hai..Too much commercialised. Both Bangash brothers were under utilised. Earlier it used to sound more organic. The same I found with pasoori too.. Beautiful composition but ruined with its sound..
This is just my opinion as a viewer..gaali mat dena

snippet.textDisplay:
होली का एक खास रङ्ग 
A rare fusion of classic and modern music.
This song is very addictive from a class of Maithili Thakur to Sheedhe Maut's rap.
Ravi Kishan at the end of the song makes me more excited.
But the most special one is the crew's everlasting smile that connects you throughout the song.
I have listened to it more than 20 times in repeated mode.
🚰🚰🚰🎸🎸🎤🎤

snippet.textDisplay: Yaar no offense to the musicians, I love Maithili's music. But ye Coke Studio india ne kya pratigya li hui hai tatti re-compositions karne ki. Itna acha gana, singer, musicians .. Usme zabardasti so called 'IN'  electronic music structure aur ye ghatiya sa rap. Chee chee. Muh mein ulti ka swad aagaya. Agar maithli ka gana nai hota to dislike bhi karte aru report spam bhi, coz ye gane ke naam pe ache gane ko spam karna hi hua. Burbak sab @cokestudioindia
